column4: Tesla to recall 11 000 Model X SUVs due to seat issue
column5: Electric carmaker Tesla Inc  is recalling 11 000 Model X sport utility vehicles worldwide due to a faulty locking mechanism in their rear seats that raises the risk of the seats falling forward in a crash.
